title: Procrastination is B.S.
itunes:title: Procrastination is B.S.
description:
Episode 242 - People always want to know how to stop procrastinating. The truth is procrastination is a fancy word for not caring. If you care about something enough, you will not procrastinate. You will get it done, it is that simple.
